OL,3,CPedestrian killed by Frontier Airlines
OL,4,Cplane taking off at Denver Airport
OL,6,FA plane taking off from Denver
OL,7,FInternational Airport hit and killed a
OL,8,Fpedestrian on the runway, authorities
OL,9,Fhave said.
OL,11,FThe accident was followed by an engine
OL,12,Ffire which forced passengers aboard
OL,13,Fthe Frontier Airlines plane to
OL,14,Fevacuate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
