OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778351318
OL,3,CPedestrian killed by Frontier Airlines
OL,4,Cplane taking off at Denver Airport
OL,6,FPilots on the plane, on route from
OL,7,FDenver to Los Angeles International
OL,8,FAirport, "reported striking a
OL,9,Fpedestrian during take-off at DEN at
OL,10,Fapproximately 11:19 p.m. on Friday,"
OL,11,Faccording to the airport's official X
OL,12,Faccount.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the airport said
OL,15,Fthe pedestrian had jumped a perimeter
OL,16,Ffence and was hit two minutes after
OL,17,Fentering the airport. They are not
OL,18,Fbelieved to have been an airport
OL,19,Femployee.
OL,26,@pD@JOUrD@dO]
