OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778351318
OL,3,CPedestrian killed by Frontier Airlines
OL,4,Cplane taking off at Denver Airport
OL,6,F"We're stopping on the runway," the
OL,7,Fpilot told the control tower according
OL,8,Fto the site ATC.com. "We just hit
OL,9,Fsomebody. We have an engine fire."
OL,11,FThe pilot is reported to have told the
OL,12,Fcontroller that they have "231 souls"
OL,13,Fon board and that an "individual was
OL,14,Fwalking across the runway".
OL,16,FThe air traffic controller responds
OL,17,Fthat they are "rolling the trucks now"
OL,18,Fbefore the pilot tells the tower they
OL,19,F"have smoke in the aircraft. We are
OL,20,Fgoing to evacuate on the runway".
