OL,3,CPedestrian killed by Frontier Airlines
OL,4,Cplane taking off at Denver Airport
OL,6,FFrontier Airlines said in a statement
OL,7,Fthat flight 4345 was the one involved
OL,8,Fin the collision and that "smoke was
OL,9,Freported in the cabin and the pilots
OL,10,Faborted take-off".
OL,12,FIt was not clear whether the smoke was
OL,13,Flinked to the crash with the
OL,14,Fpedestrian.
OL,16,FFrontier Airlines said the plane was
OL,17,Fcarrying 224 passengers and seven crew
OL,18,Fmembers. Passengers were evacuated via
OL,19,Fslides and the emergency crew bused
OL,20,Fthem to the terminal.
OL,26,@pD@[OUrD@QO]
