OL,3,CPedestrian killed by Frontier Airlines
OL,4,Cplane taking off at Denver Airport
OL,6,FThe airport spokesperson said 12
OL,7,Fpassengers suffered minor injuries and
OL,8,Ffive were taken to local hospitals.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,F"We are investigating this incident
OL,16,Fand gathering more information in
OL,17,Fcoordination with the airport and
OL,18,Fother safety authorities," the airline
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@ZO]
