OL,3,CPedestrian killed by Frontier Airlines
OL,4,Cplane taking off at Denver Airport
OL,6,FThe incident came one day after a
OL,7,FDelta Air Lines employee was killed
OL,8,Fwhile on the job at the Orlando
OL,9,FInternational Airport.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the airline said the
OL,12,Femployee was killed Thursday night
OL,13,Fwithout providing details of the
OL,14,Fincident or the name of the employee.
OL,16,F"We are focused on extending our full
OL,17,Fsupport to family and taking care of
OL,18,Four Orlando team during this difficult
OL,19,Ftime," the airline said.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@FO]
